ROYAL TAX LIEN SERVICES, L.L.C. d/b/a Crusader Lien Services, L.L.C, Plaintiff,
v.
Syeda Fatima SHUAIB and Syed Tariq Shuaib, Defendants-Movants,
and
Hilltop Fuel Heating & A/C, and Discover Bank, Defendants. M-1436 September Term 2017
M-1437 September Term 2017
079532 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-1436) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-1437) is denied.
